---
import { footerLinks } from "../data/navigation";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<footer class="border-t border-border bg-bg-subtle">
  <div class="container-content py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <span
            class="grid size-8 place-items-center rounded-[0.6rem] bg-brand text-on-brand"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <img
              src="/dionomy_logo.svg"
              alt=""
              width="24"
              height="24"
              aria-hidden="true"
            />
          </span>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-fg">Dionomy</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
          성인 취미 학원이 더 이상 수강생을 조용히 잃지 않도록.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="flex flex-col gap-3" aria-label="푸터">
        <p class="text-[0.8rem] font-semibold text-fg-subtle">바로가기</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          {
            footerLinks.map((link) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={link.href}
                  class="text-[0.92rem] text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-brand"
                >
                  {link.label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <p class="text-[0.8rem] font-semibold text-fg-subtle">문의</p>
        <a
          href={`mailto:${site.email}`}
          class="text-[0.92rem] text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-brand"
        >
          {site.email}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-border pt-6 text-[0.8rem] text-fg-faint sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"
    >
      <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {site.legalName}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
